description: The land water content data used to create this images were generated from The Global Land Data Assimilation System (GLDAS). GLDAS outputs land water content by using numerous land surface models and data assimilation. For more information on GLDAS please visit http://gcmd.nasa.gov/records/GCMD_GES_DISC_GLDAS_NOAH10SUBP_3H_V001.html. The images are available on monthly 1 degree grids in GIF format. This total water content is directly comparable to what GRACE measures over land. The Greenland values should NOT be used, the model is not valid there.
name: TELLUS GLDAS LAND WATER CONTENT IMAGES
